longBusinessSummary: Fireweed Zinc Ltd. acquires, explores for, and develops mineral properties in Canada. It explores for zinc, lead, and silver deposits. The company owns interest in the Macmillan Pass project covering an area of approximately 544 square kilometers located in Yukon, Canada. Fireweed Zinc Ltd. was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
